<task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/">
<title>Replacing the battery</title>
<prolog/>
<taskbody>
<context>You may wish to upgrade your phone to a higher-capacity battery, or 
you may need to replace the rechargeable
battery when it can no longer hold a charge.</context>
<steps>
<step>
<cmd>Remove the rear battery cover.</cmd></step>
<step>
<cmd>Remove the battery.</cmd></step>
<step>
<cmd>Replace the battery.</cmd></step>
<step>
<cmd>Replace the rear battery cover.</cmd></step></steps></taskbody></task>
